","msg":"咁pk"},{"pid":"b3cf958eba7505aab8e464111361e33ac3e77db6","tid":1608012,"uid":139931,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"246450e60c231e02e5751afb851438aa2df1b6a1","tid":1608012,"uid":158889,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T06:48:54.000Z","msg":"慢慢黎 唔好急 遊擊唔係陣地 唔洗打得漂亮"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T06:50:04.000Z","msg":"遊街定遊擊呀 d狗未佈好陣就要打啦 仲係到鳩流流"},{"pid":"a848d84204f4ed47395c657bfcac7ec088c0ed7d","tid":1608012,"uid":5216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T06:53:59.000Z","msg":"幫支共賀国慶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n612 721 811 831 929 101 新屋嶺 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f07c93558d45dae776fd6cb87eeac63c56a555df","tid":1608012,"uid":271434,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T06:54:42.000Z","msg":"<strong>我以颱風風眼橫過比喻，預測閱兵期間香港唔會發生衝突</strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">昨日警察不斷恐嚇大家十一唔好出，同埋有很多假消息話各地暴徒會燒商場，呢個奇怪現象同早幾日批不反對通知書後立即大搜捕完全不同，<span style=\"color: red;\">就係因為警察知道，十一當日唔可以捉人、唔可以出現血腥畫面，</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">但中共又唔容許有大量人上街反共反雜，所以先嚇定大家。<br />\n</span><br />\n現在就好似颱風風眼即將略過時候，警察瘋狂捉人，製造白色恐怖。<span style=\"color: red;\">風眼將會在閱兵期間橫過香港，忽然晴天萬里，到時候社會上一定太平無事，警察唔會拉人，大家可以放膽出街。</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">但要小心，當10月1日半夜過後，就有可能好似風眼過後，又出現狂風暴雨，</span>所以大家意見表達完結後，就盡快返歸，唔好戀戰。<br />\n<br />\n點解警察聽日閱兵期間唔捉人？<span style=\"color: gold;\">因為北大人唔想在世界各地直播閱兵期間，同時直播出現血腥鎮壓嘅場面，咁會落佢面，令雜種即時受到黨內外以及西方社會譴責，</span>所以十一閱兵嘅時候唔會清場鎮壓。<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\">聽講呢個安排僅十一閱兵嘅時段限定！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1606271\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1606271</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n今日香港慘劇係雜種一手造成，冤有頭債有主，請大家對準政權目標<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有明確訊息證實係習近平一人當日堅持拒絕「撤回」及下令將44人極速起訴暴動！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1602129\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1602129</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">十一遊行要高叫「天滅中共！習近平全家死」口號落中共面！</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1568634\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1568634</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ab8782c3b9dba155e6c9aca92831e47eeca72286","tid":1608012,"uid":158889,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b3cf958eba7505aab8e464111361e33ac3e77db6","tid":1608012,"uid":139931,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"246450e60c231e02e5751afb851438aa2df1b6a1","tid":1608012,"uid":158889,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T06:48:54.000Z","msg":"慢慢黎 唔好急 遊擊唔係陣地 唔洗打得漂亮"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T06:50:04.000Z","msg":"遊街定遊擊呀 d狗未佈好陣就要打啦 仲係到鳩流流"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T06:56:07.000Z","msg":"無人一出師就最top 個班 知道自己做緊乜就得"},{"pid":"981c9547ab9f245dc2ad3350ae03755bb7b16c4f","tid":1608012,"uid":30506,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"b7e3338c4f74037fd63a4d83aafd67c60e5c7fb4","tid":1608012,"uid":139931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T06:44:21.000Z","msg":"聚到人又唔做野 其他區打到仆街 荃灣咁少狗都唔攻"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T07:00:00.000Z","msg":"不指責，態度可以改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b4e954312075cba9a159bda117b0062ce3231c4","tid":1608012,"uid":53003,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c2d4909432f2ec92b011e3c056fd69b53dd376d7","tid":1608012,"uid":144626,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T06:48:16.000Z","msg":"黃大仙今日都唔多掂"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-01T07:01:08.000Z","msg":"黃大仙一早已經重兵"},{"pid":"4ff12610e0870467a341c92e7d2e6bc7f50d4